      "description": "Offering a mechanically sorted BMW E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six powerplant. This example boasts exceptional throttle linearity via its individual throttle bodies and a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. The chassis remains composed thanks to reinforced subframe mounts and a recently serviced Double VANOS system, ensuring variable valve timing remains within factory specifications. Equipped with the M-variable differential lock for superior power delivery through the corners, the car exhibits a minor road patina consistent with its driver-focused history. Suspension kinematics are sharp, with refreshed bushings and dampers providing a taut, communicative ride. A structurally sound, high-performance icon for the discerning driver.",
